name: MSRI-SIX-GIFRainbow-IWh-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-SIX-GIFRainbow-IWh-01" Is a six projection artwork. There are 6 gif animations of a one 3d Object which is  generated with custom definition. 1 loft is animated in 1 layer in Rainbow colors. The cells of the Indigo  "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the loft. Another one white  flat cube is rotating. Order of projection is from upper left to down right is: Left, Front, Top, Bottom, Back, Right.  Total 64 frames, 1024*1536 px canvas.
